"96",96,"Charlotte Linlin / Big Mom",880,68,4.388e+09,"Captain","living",53,"Big Mom's crew","assets",NA,11121500000,TRUE,"Fruit of Souls","Allows you to manipulate the souls of human beings as you wish. The user can introduce a soul into an object or animal to bring it to life and humanize it, i.e. give it consciousness and the gift of speech. These beings are called 'Homies'. The user can also divide his or her own soul into fragments that live on as avatars of the fruit eater. The main role of these avatars is to harvest fragments of life from living beings and redistribute them to their owners. People with no fear of death or psychic powers are more resistant to this fruit.","Paramecia"
"97",97,"Charlotte Dent-de-chien",509,48,1.057e+09,"General Sucré","living",53,"Big Mom's crew","assets",NA,11121500000,TRUE,"Glutinous Rice Fruit","Allows the user to generate glutinous rice at will. This allows the user to block anyone's attacks and trap them in a large quantity of glutinous rice. What's more, it has several similarities with the Gum Gum fruit, such as elongating limbs and blocking all gunfire. However, the substance dissolves after receiving a large quantity of water. It's a special Paramecia.","Paramecia"
