"101",101,"Charlotte Daifuku",489,48,3e+08,"Lieutenant","living",53,"Big Mom's crew","assets",NA,11121500000,TRUE,"Fruit of the Lamp","Enables the user to summon a powerful genie from his body and attack opponents with it. This genie is armed with a halberd.","Paramecia"
