"370",370,"Sugar",110,22,NA,"Lieutenant of the Trebol Army","living",21,"Don Quixote's crew","inactive",23,1.113e+09,FALSE,"Fruit du Joujou","Transforms any person into a toy by simply touching them. Transformed people no longer have control over their bodies and obey orders given to them (at least, if the user has given them any). The effects of this fruit stop the growth of its user the moment he eats it. People turned into toys are forgotten, all memories of them disappear and they are preserved from aging. If the user falls unconscious, all the people become themselves again, and the memories of those who had forgotten them resurface.","Paramecia"
